02:24:28,760 --> 02:24:29,760
Such actions can be a-

2071
02:24:30,000 --> 02:24:35,639
proved as an expression of love and the self-determination of the donor.

2072
02:24:35,639 --> 02:24:42,559
In all cases, respect for the body of the donor should be maintained."

